<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BMW</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --dark: #ffffff;
            --silver: #000000;
            --accent: #ffffff;
            --light-gray: #000000;
            --white: #1b89b8;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
            color: var(--dark);
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .navbar {
            background: var(--dark) !important;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .navbar-brand {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: var(--white) !important;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .navbar-brand span {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            color: var(--silver) !important;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover,
        .navbar-nav .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--white) !important;
        }

        .navbar-toggler {
            border-color: var(--silver);
        }

        .navbar-toggler-icon {
            filter: invert(1);
        }

        .site-header {
            background: var(--dark);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2rem;
        }

        .site-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .site-header h3 {
            font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--silver);
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 3rem 4rem;
            gap: 3rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-text {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .hero-text h2 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.3;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .hero-text p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }

        .hero-image {
            flex: 0 0 420px;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .carousel-section {
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .carousel-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: var(--dark);
        }

        #carouselExampleIndicators {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .carousel-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 450px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .carousel-caption {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .carousel-caption h5 {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .carousel-control-prev-icon,
        .carousel-control-next-icon {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            background-size: 50%;
        }

        footer {
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--silver);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--accent);
        }

        footer strong {
            color: var(--white);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-section {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .hero-image {
                flex: unset;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .site-header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .carousel-item img {
                height: 280px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"> MOTOS <span>BMW</span></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="#">Inicio</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Inventario</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Servicios</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Acerca de</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">Contacto</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="site-header">
        <h1>MOTOS BMW</h1>
        <h3>SAMUEL HERNANDEZ BENITEZ</h3>
    </header>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>Venta de motos BMW.</h2>
            <p>1. Ofrecemos motos BMW certificadas y con garantía extendida para una mejor experiencia.</p>
            <p>2. Financiamiento y el mejor servicio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="s1000rr.avif" 
                 alt="La mejor moto del mundo, s1000rr" 
                 class="img-fluid rounded shadow"
                 style="width:100%; height:280px; object-fit:cover;">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="carousel-section">
        <h2> Inventario </h2>

        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-indicators">
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="r-1250-gs-adventure.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>BMW GS 1250R Adventur</h5>
                        <p>Potencia en cada viaje.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="bmw-g-310-r.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>BMW G31O</h5>
                        <p>Lujo y potencia para el uso diario.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="bmw-k-1600-b-2022.jpg">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>BMW R 1250 RT</h5>
                        <p>Potencia y seguridad para viajes largos.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; <strong>Motos BMW</strong> &mdash; Samuel Hernandez Benitez. Derechos reservados.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
